data.description: PRICE REDUCED for this Entertainer's Paradise!  The large living room flows easily into the great room with a custom-built fireplace.  Granite counters top an impressive amount of cabinets in the spacious kitchen featuring heated tile floors.  Anchoring this space is the central dining room with french doors that lead to al fresco dining on the back deck.  Upstairs are two bedrooms, a bathroom, a large bonus room/office/???, and the HUGE primary-suite with sitting area and walk-in closet.  Ensuite bathroom includes a large jetted tub, walk-in shower, and water closet--and those heated floors! Fully-fenced backyard has several fruit trees, garden space, shed, and RV parking in addition to the large deck.  Please ask about financing options.
